  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC458">
        <l>muṉṉatti ṉuṇaruṅ kiḷaviyu muḷavē.</l>
	<l>yiṉṉa veṉṉuñ coṉmuṟai yāṉa.</l>
            </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/255/mode/1up">255</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/256/mode/1up">256</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, ituvum coṟkaṇṇatōr poruḷpaṭutal vēṟṟumai yuṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : colliṉaviṭattuc coṟkiṭantavāṟē kuṟippiṉāṟkoṇṭu uṇarappaṭum poruḷumuḷa; coṟkaḷatiyāṇṭāyiṉum maṟṟu iṉṉaveṉṟu taṉmai vēṟupāṭu collutaṉ muṟaikkaṇ eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC458-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'ceñcevi veḷḷokkalar'</l></lg>
<p>eṉavum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC458-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'kuḻaikoṇṭu kōḻiyeṟiyum vāḻkkaiyar'</l></lg>
<p>eṉavum varum.</p>
<p>ceñcevi veḷḷokkalar eṉṟāl, utirañ coriyuñ ceviyar, veḷiya cuṟṟattār eṉpatu aṉṟu; ceviyellāñ cālaccempoṉ aṇintu, muṭṭil celvattākkiṉaiyuṭaiyar eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>'kuḻaikoṇṭu kōḻi yeṟiyum' eṉṟakkālum, kōḻiyeṟitaleṉṟu uṇaraṟpālatu, muṭṭil celvattār eṉpatu uṇaraṟpāṟṟu.	(62)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

